the alleged bribe was a flagrant example of the socalled 
money politics that underlie the recruit scandal with 
reverberations to the top of japanese politics and in the stock 
market as well 
a camera hidden by nippon television network with narazakis 
permission showed matsubara asking the opposition parliamentarian 
