illegal but the scandal called sharp attention to political ethics 
and intimate links between business and politics 
the opposition and ruling parties all need money to run election 
campaigns constituency affairs and parliamentary activities and 
big business has always been a major source of cash in japans 
rapidly expanding economy new companies like recruitcosmos have 
become a source of political money through the device of selling 
shares at bargain prices before they go public 
but never before has the practice made so many headlines or 
administered such a jolt 
the opposition japan socialist party demanded miyazawas 
resignation but the finance minister has refused takeshita who 
needs miyazawa to quarterback a taxreform package through the 
diet has said miyazawa bears an ethical responsibility but 
resignation was not called for 
