no independent confirmation was available of the mujahedeen 
report the movement claimed last month that an estimated 1200 
political prisoners had been killed in iran since midsummer 
irans official news media monitored in cyprus have reported 
that scores of counterrevolutionaries and iraqi spies were 
executed by firing squad or publicly hanged in several cities over 
the last two months 
but the londonbased human rights group amnesty international 
