complicating that situation he said i think were going to 
see a continuation of the decline of the russian empire which 
must be handled with caution 
he and dukakis would offer a creative partnership between 
business and government not an industrial policy bentsen said 
asked by reporters to elaborate on his statement about the 
soviets bentsen said we see their economy in a shambles and 
people demanding something be done about the standard of living and 
that they have a reasonable amount of consumer goods 
you see them backing off around the world and you see the 
american economic system being adopted more and more in other 
countries youre seeing a serious decline setting in on the 
russian empire he said 
we have to handle that with considerable care he added 
there is a tendency when one is going into a decline for the 
military to strike out its important that we keep our defenses 
strong during that process 
bentsen received a polite reception from the michigan luncheon 
