7482 cents a pound feeder cattle were unchanged to 45 cent 
higher with october at 8190 cents a pound hogs were unchanged to 
42 cent lower with december at 4145 cents a pound frozen pork 
bellies were 37 cent lower to 55 cent higher with february at 
4935 cents a pound 
