previous weeks 1797 million tons the american iron and steel 
institute reported monday 
the industrys production amounted to 866 percent of capacity 
during the week compared with 838 percent in the previous week 
estimated figures for the year to date showed production at 
80945 million net tons an increase of 161 percent from the 
69725 million net tons in the previous year 
production so far this year used 894 percent of capacity 
compared with 770 percent a year earlier 
